data.title: Confederate Monuments & Memory in Baltimore
data.meta_description: This timeline on the history of Confederate memory and the removal of Confederate Monuments in Baltimore is based on research and writing by Eli Pousson.
data.text: This timeline includes some of the same information found in our more general Civil War memory in Maryland timeline. Please help us improve this timeline by sharing suggestions, comments, and questions on our Google Sheet for this timeline. We created this timeline using Timeline JS.
